      "raw_text": "The secretary was instructed to\nget In touch with the state grange\non this matter that the farmers of\nthis section of Washington may be\nnotified to take advantage of the\nmarket privileges to sell their pro-\nducts direct to consumers. At pres\nent they have to accept any price\noffered them and the consumer has\nto pay any price asked by the COM\nmission men. Under the new con-\ndition of affairs proposed this state\nof affairs will be done away with."
